1228
01:46:08,037 --> 01:46:09,868
Run?

1229
01:46:13,076 --> 01:46:14,976
Get the horses out, quick

1230
01:46:16,146 --> 01:46:17,113
Hurry up

1231
01:46:17,580 --> 01:46:19,912
Kill all those who run

1232
01:46:27,190 --> 01:46:28,157
Go

