1238
01:46:41,871 --> 01:46:43,065
await for my command

1239
01:46:43,106 --> 01:46:44,073
Yes

1240
01:47:01,558 --> 01:47:03,185
General

1241
01:47:03,226 --> 01:47:04,955
it's over

1242
01:47:04,994 --> 01:47:06,552
