1243
01:47:06,596 --> 01:47:07,756
surrender

1244
01:47:07,797 --> 01:47:09,025
We can't surrender...

1245
01:47:09,065 --> 01:47:10,896
General, Ge Li said

1246
01:47:10,934 --> 01:47:13,425
