1258
01:47:50,673 --> 01:47:51,731
Let's go

1259
01:48:06,322 --> 01:48:07,755
General...

1260
01:48:07,790 --> 01:48:09,189
run...

1261
01:48:13,429 --> 01:48:15,488
This person is the great General Niu

1262
01:49:19,996 --> 01:49:20,963
Commander

1263
01:49:20,997 --> 01:49:24,455
