1292
01:51:26,622 --> 01:51:28,590
and protect our homeland

1293
01:51:29,592 --> 01:51:31,583
Isn't that just another battle field?

1294
01:51:31,627 --> 01:51:34,755
There's only victory & defeat

1295
01:51:36,165 --> 01:51:38,531
