1297
01:51:40,870 --> 01:51:43,202
Ge Li had lost

1298
01:51:43,239 --> 01:51:47,938
His theory is impractical,
idealism leads to jealousy

1299
01:51:48,978 --> 01:51:51,105
He can't even gain the trust

1300
01:51:51,147 --> 01:51:53,411
