1347
01:54:58,567 --> 01:55:00,626
but at least...

1348
01:55:00,670 --> 01:55:02,399
now...

1349
01:55:02,438 --> 01:55:04,338
I can kill you

1350
01:55:04,373 --> 01:55:06,238
