1372
01:58:01,016 --> 01:58:02,608
That way

1373
01:58:14,163 --> 01:58:15,391
Ask yourself

1374
01:58:17,600 --> 01:58:19,397
Is it for the soldiers

1375
01:58:19,435 --> 01:58:21,596
